Dear Real Estate Agent,

Do you want to earn $70,000 a year selling 24 homes? I know you’ve been doing all the “right” things so far in your real estate career. Most agents spend time listening to podcasts, watching training videos, and going to training events all in hopes of bettering yourself so you can earn more money.

It’s a fact that 87% of real estate agents fail within their first 5 years in the business because they run out of money, get too distracted, and don’t have the guidance or mentorship they need to succeed.
It’s likely that you’re working for a broker, but not getting the training and support you need. So, now, you’ve landed on this page looking for more. For that, I congratulate you! Everyone knows that if you don’t build up a consistent pipeline of listings (or even buyers), the money runs out—and that causes all kinds of problems. You don’t want this to happen. Let’s just get that thought out of your head!

I can provide you with the training, support, mentorship, accountability, and tools you need to build a consistent and reliable income in real estate.
Working on my team gets you a full CRM (Customer Relationship Management software, $200 value), at least 30 leads per month ($500 value), broker support ($5,000 value), and inside sales support (ISAs) to qualify your leads ($1,000 value).  My team has highly trained, licensed agents that will qualify your leads and set appointments for you!  In the month of January (2018) my team members had 84 qualified appointments set for them from our ISAs.
These are all things that you have to pay for yourself or figure out on your own as an independent agent, but you won’t have to pay for any of these things with us! We provide you with every tool you will need, at no cost to you. This means that you will have the software and the systems to manage all of your contacts so that no opportunities fall through the cracks. You won’t have to rely on cold calls alone to get your business. You will be confident in your deal-making ability to close homes because we will guide you through every step of the way. You’ll have someone to follow up with your leads and set appointments for you! How good does all of that sound?
You can do it yourself and take the risk, but you may not be in the position to do that. You can join another company that charges a flat fee, but you won’t get the leads and support.
I recently took on an agent that had been licensed for one year and worked with another large real estate office here in the Des Moines area. In his first year, he closed one home. Greg just finished his first year on my team, and he sold 53 homes and made over $130,000, with NO MONTHLY EXPENSES. 
I took on another new agent (from the same company that Greg worked for) and again, same story. One year in the business, less than three closings, and she just wasn’t making it. Katie has now been with our team for a year and has closed over 25 deals and earned $75,000, with NO MONTHLY EXPENSES. She’s hoping to double her production this year!
Another great success story is that of Jason. He joined my team about 18 months ago. Same story. Had his license for about year, didn’t have a pipeline built up, and he wasn’t making it in real estate. Jason joined my team and closed over 40 deals last year, earning well over $100,000, with NO MONTHLY EXPENSES! 
Do you see the trend?  We want our team members to earn a great income, with NO MONTHLY EXPENSES.
